            <h2>Workout Routines</h2>
            <p>Here are a few workout routines to get you started:</p>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Beginner:</strong> 30 minutes of brisk walking, 3 times a week.</li>
                <li><strong>Intermediate:</strong> Circuit training combining cardio and weights, 4 times a week.</li>
                <li><strong>Advanced:</strong> High-Intensity Interval Training (HIIT) and strength training, 5 times a week.</li>
            </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
            <h2>Nutrition Advice</h2>
